{ Mining pools

 In order to mine → development/Crypto-Currencies/Bitcoin/coin[bitcoins] more efficiently, it's probably best to
 join a mining pool.
 -
 When the pool, using their combined effort, has successfully mined bitcoins, they're divided among the pool members.

